    <h2>About Us</h2>
<p><span style="font-size: 120%;"><em>&#8220;Cascade Specialties, Inc. is the Premier Manufacturer &amp; Supplier of naturally grown,&nbsp; extra-low bacteria conventional &amp; organic dehydrated onion products worldwide.&#8221;</em></span></p>
<p><span><span style="color: black;">Since our founding in 1993 we&nbsp;</span><span style="color: black;">have been committed to producing quality dehydrated onions. &nbsp;Now u</span></span><span style="color: black;"><span style="color: #000000;">nder Jain Irrigation Systems ownership, we continue to produce the same high quality products from seed to harvest.&nbsp;&nbsp; We accomplish this </span></span><span style="color: black;">by:</span></p>
<ul style="color: #181818;">
<li><span style="color: #000000;">Working with local growers.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #000000;"><span style="color: black;">Monitoring crop development.</span>&nbsp;</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #000000;">Using optimum harvesting &amp; production techniques.</span></li>
<li><span style="color: #000000;">Building cutting-edge, climate-controlled storage facilities.</span></li>
</ul>
<p><span style="color: #000000;">Our work is concluded only upon satisfactory delivery of our products to our customers.</span></p>
<p><span style="color: black;"><br />Employing this hands-on philosophy at our facilities in the state of Oregon, aided by the latest technology,&nbsp;we can trace our products to the very field from which they were grown.&nbsp;</span></p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><span style="color: black;">&nbsp;</span></p>


  


